{"tid":1464776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無限期佔領機場 直至政府正面回應","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:28.000Z","uid":167355,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03694da7ba14cab42e9fcf99524532fb1e010ca6","tid":1464776,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"相信大家地知五大訴求 我整合小小愚見<br />\n<br />\n有手足提過我地要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">輸出既係WHAT WE WANT！</span></span></strong>我地係抗爭緊既人係會知「光復香港 時代革命」但既然我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想打國際牌 </span></span></strong>係咪要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面輸出訴求？</span></span></strong>而並非強調黑警濫權 當然黑警既犯法行為令人法指<br />\n<br />\n當好多人話block人check in 既時候 話停你飛失民意 我想同大家講 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地係同全世界講清楚 因為政府無視訴求而出現今日機場無限期佔領 責任在於政府 非手無寸鐵的市民</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有 五大訴求 我唔知好定唔好 <br />\n但係一齊整合 唔好屌住先<br />\n<br />\n第一，撤回逃犯條例～老實說，柒婆話左「壽終正寢」，順住個波玩，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求「壽終正寢」成為有法律效力既詞語</span></strong></span>，亦即是<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">等同「撤回」</span></span></strong>一樣既效力。咁就當你「壽終正寢」囉～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，成立獨立調查委員會～柒婆話有現行機制嘛，唔想成立，唔會割席，我個人覺得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>改革比成立容易</strong></span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然而家同樣好難</span>，而大家都知鉛水調查完，又係無事。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求警方人員及前警方，不能成為監警會委員，</span></strong></span>而監警會由不同人士擔任，共同處理，如前高官～陳太？法官？等（因為我真係好蠢，所以唔該集思廣益），只係查警察。只係第一步，之後發現唔對路，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">重新要求成立獨立調查委員會。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三，釋放所有被捕人士～基於警方有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>暴力傾向</strong></span></span>，因此釋放被捕人士係保障市民人生安全，係現在香港，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察存在完全威脅市民生命安危，因此釋放係基於人權考慮。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第四，撤銷被捕者控罪～因為太多太多濫捕情況出現，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警察同律政司選擇性執法</span></strong></span>，令到市民對施政好失望，失去公信力，而被控罪行，更係胡亂控罪。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不能容忍香港政府，破壞法治</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n第五，立即實行真普選～我個人覺得呢個係最後一步，而機制係點我真係唔清楚，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出既時候要講明</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我只係希望係由自己選出既人，管治我地，還政於民。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，謹記，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">輸出係要what we want！</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一切行動皆因政府無視，以及縱容警方暴力治港。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無限期佔領機場 <br />\n我係香港政府 無視市民</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"77eeef72f255f0b2cb861959c5c5244de0e0af78","tid":1464776,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:19.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"6ed689aa2b3f0e22b0787b058f27dae3c8cc0cd6","tid":1464776,"uid":294783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"警亂打市民，咁即係市民被迫無法離開機場啦!<br />\n<br />\n咁市民咪唔走囉，就係咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n政府仲要基於人道理由提供食物添!<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒喎"},{"pid":"8195c447bc5fe21432d75357cd5c19697cb661d6","tid":1464776,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"4ed482cb5ea2b0a6e36c96707462f5ddd31b338c","tid":1464776,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"a5edd9560fd8059a3ebcd80758cf7c1ccd6feab0","tid":1464776,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s